reviewText: This DVD features a few great Mickey Mouse Clubhouse episodes (one that has never been seen yet on air) and is perfect for any Mickey fan.  My boys love that they can watch Mickey and the gang anytime they want and now anywhere since it comes with a Digital Copy (meaning you can load the disc on your iPad, iPod or mobile device very quickly and easily!)  The episodes are space-themed and there is 70 minutes full of fun plus bonus features!  You can also use the Mickey Mote with this DVD for more fun!
Title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Space Adventure

reviewText: Grand Daughter Loves the Mickey Mouse Club House "Junior" DVD's. She enjoys watching and it helps her fall asleep at night.
Title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Space Adventure

reviewText: My family has been a fan of Mickey Mouse and in particular Mickey Mouse Clubhouse for some time. This DVD has some great new episodes that are both educational and fun and I can tell you that my girls just loved them! Not only do you get to see your favorite Disney Characters in some funny situations, but you also get to go on some great adventures as well. If you are a fan of Disney, Mickey Mouse, or any of his Disney pals, you will love this new DVD and so will your family!
Title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Space Adventure

reviewText: Gift for my 3 year old granddaughter who is now almost 7.  My memory of this is nil.  6 years ago is when my son came home from Iraq, and he and his wife went to Disney World Florida.  They were sad because their daughter would have loved to see the clubhouse.  Their children stayed home.
summary: Six years ago is a long time to remember even buying it.
Title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Space Adventure

reviewText: Clay loves the DVD. After his second trip to Disney World, he's all about Mickey Mouse and all the others. Thanks. Kathy
Title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Space Adventure

reviewText: Bought this for my daughter.  When playing the dvd in my car it has a very long pause at the beginning.
Title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Space Adventure

reviewText: I have a grandson who absolutely loves Mickey Mouse so I currently have 13 Mickey Mouse DVDs in my collection (mainly so I don't go insane watching the same Mickey Mouse movie over and over with my grandson!).  Normally he is glued to the screen from start to finish for anything Mickey Mouse related he watches; however, this one he walked away from and never came back.  It really was a bit boring.  What can I say?  Sorry Mickey!  We still love you...just not this episode.
Title: Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Space Adventure
